      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so if i switch to a generator it stays low. but i'm also seeing these weird spikes in my RAM usage where it just jumps up for no reason for a few seconds then drops. is that just part of how python handles garbage collection or is there something else that could be eating up the resources?",
